---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="BVI 官方资源导航 | BVI.vg" description="BVI 官方与权威机构资源汇总：FSC、ITA、FIA、EU Council及国际标准组织的英文官方入口。">
  <div class="max-w-(--content-max-width) mx-auto px-6 py-10">
    <article class="prose">
      <h1>BVI 官方资源导航</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-muted">以下为本网站内容撰写所参考的主要官方与权威来源，供读者自行核实和深入研究。</p>

      <h2>BVI 监管机构</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="border border-border-main rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="!text-base !mt-0 !mb-1">BVI Financial Services Commission（FSC）</h3>
          <p class="!text-sm text-text-muted">金融服务监管机构。负责公司注册、注册代理人监管、受监管实体查询。</p>
          <a href="https://www.bvifsc.vg/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="!text-sm">bvifsc.vg</a>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-border-main rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="!text-base !mt-0 !mb-1">BVI International Tax Authority（ITA）</h3>
          <p class="!text-sm text-text-muted">主管经济实质申报、CRS、FATCA、国别报告（CbCR）及跨境税务信息交换。</p>
          <a href="https://bviita.vg/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="!text-sm">bviita.vg</a>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-border-main rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="!text-base !mt-0 !mb-1">BVI Financial Investigation Agency（FIA）</h3>
          <p class="!text-sm text-text-muted">负责反洗钱（AML）、反恐融资（CFT）和金融犯罪调查相关事务。</p>
          <a href="https://www.bvifia.vg/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="!text-sm">bvifia.vg</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>国际组织与标准</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="border border-border-main rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="!text-base !mt-0 !mb-1">EU Council — EU list of non-cooperative jurisdictions</h3>
          <p class="!text-sm text-text-muted">欧盟税务非合作司法管辖区名单。持续动态监测，最近修订为 2026 年 2 月。</p>
          <a href="https://www.consilium.europa.eu/en/policies/eu-list-of-non-cooperative-jurisdictions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="!text-sm">consilium.europa.eu</a>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-border-main rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="!text-base !mt-0 !mb-1">OECD — Tax Transparency</h3>
          <p class="!text-sm text-text-muted">OECD 税务透明标准、CRS 实施框架及有害税收实践论坛（FHTP）。</p>
          <a href="https://www.oecd.org/en/topics/global-tax-and-transparency.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="!text-sm">oecd.org</a>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-border-main rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="!text-base !mt-0 !mb-1">FATF — Financial Action Task Force</h3>
          <p class="!text-sm text-text-muted">反洗钱与反恐融资国际标准制定机构。</p>
          <a href="https://www.fatf-gafi.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="!text-sm">fatf-gafi.org</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
